CustomField.description: The API name of a field set used by the Milestone object. Fields in this set define the milestone fields (if associated milestones exist) to copy from the template to the new project. These fields are not shown on the Create Project from Template page. The default value is CreateProjFromTempAltCopyMilestoneFields.
